  "texts": [
    "The first question is quintessentially connected to an appropriate conceptualisation of manipulation.",
    "Answering it will give us a way to tell whether a given influence-such as an output produced by a generative AI application-is manipulation.",
    "For example, suppose that a personal digital health assistant driven by generative AI outputs 'You should be ashamed of yourself for ordering that meal' to the user after drawing on their recent purchase history.",
    "To decide whether that prompt-or any other output generated by the system-qualifies as manipulation, we need reliable criteria to identify manipulation.",
    "In this section, I will briefly review the most pertinent criteria for manipulation."
  ],
